gw.api.databuilder

Class ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<ReturnPremiumHandlingScheme,ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder>
      • gw.api.databuilder.ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<ReturnPremiumHandlingScheme>

    public class ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder
extends DataBuilder<ReturnPremiumHandlingScheme,ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder>
    Defines a builder for a ReturnPremiumHandlingScheme, which should not be used to create instances but instead should be passed to a ReturnPremiumPlanBuilder to specify the values set on one of the ReturnPremiumPlan instance's scheme's. Return premium handling schemes are defined only in the context of a ReturnPremiumPlan and are automatically created by it when it is created. Use the ReturnPremiumPlanBuilder.withHandlingScheme(gw.bc.invoice.typekey.ReturnPremiumHandlingCondition, ReturnPremiumHandlingSchemeBuilder) method to associate a return premium handling scheme builder with a ReturnPremiumPlanBuilder for the specified ReturnPremiumHandlingCondition, which will support applying its values to the associated return premium handling scheme when the return premium plan is created.
